title: Affordable, Spacious & Unbeatable 3 Bedroom Apartment Home!
posting_body: ['You get the best of the small town and city feels here at Windy Ridge Apartments in Austin, TX.', 'Our property is minutes away both from Lake Travis and nearby entertainment such as shopping and dining!', 'Our one, two, and three bedroom units are affordable, updated, and ready for you to call home.', 'Each unit features central air conditioning, walk in closets, and private balconies or patios.', 'Our community gets to enjoy amenities such as our swimming pool with sundeck, community clubhouse with a kitchen, and a playground.', 'IMPORTANT NOTE: Leasing Office Open - By Appointment Only.', 'Voucher Holders Welcome!', 'Please Call For Pricing & Information.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Swimming Pool With Sundeck', '- Washer & Dryer Connections', '- Playground', '- Dishwasher', '- Master Walk-In Closet', '- Private Entrances', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Windy Ridge participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $46,380 | 2 Occupants: $52,980 | 3', 'Occupants: $59,580 | 4 Occupants: $66,180 | 5 Occupants: $71,520 | 6 Occupants: $76,800.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community;\xa0credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Tuesday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Thursday-Friday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Windy Ridge', '10910 N FM 620', 'Austin, TX, 78726', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '1S7IGzP6HvzZ']
